Smart Packaging and Sustainability
Smart packaging also supports sustainability. Flexible packaging uses less plastic and energy compared to rigid packaging like bottles and jars. When smart features are added, brands can:
Reduce food and product waste
Improve recycling through digital sorting
Share eco-friendly tips with customers
For example, digital watermarks hidden in a package can help recycling machines separate plastic better, leading to cleaner recycling streams.

